    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require food labels to clearly indicate if food products contain alcohol",
        "additional_details": "It would make life so much easier and would mean less time running through every ingredients list on every food product whilst shopping, if there was a mandatory identifying label for alcohol such as \"A\". This would be useful for anyone who does not wish to consume alcohol in any form, but in particular for Muslims.",
        "background": "It is normally easy to identify if a food product is suitable for vegetarians because of the much-recognised \"V\" symbol. As a Muslim, I often select such products, only to read the ingredients list and discover that they contain alcohol, the consumption of which is forbidden in Islam.",
